Load Balancing Types:

i) Breadth-first: Aims to evenly distribute new user sessions across session hosts in a host pool. You don't have to specify a maximum session limit for the number of sessions.

ii) Depth-first: Keeps starting new user sessions on one session host until the maximum session limit is reached.

